---
import { Icons } from "../components/iconify/icons";
import Iconify from "../components/iconify/iconify.astro";
import Logo from "../assets/logo.svg";
import CardIcon from "../components/card/card-icon.astro";
import StackIcon from "../components/card/stack-icon.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div
  class="h-svh md:h-screen w-full px-5 py-10 md:px-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-evenly gap-8"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-5">
    <h2
      class="bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary to-primary bg-clip-text text-transparent font-bold text-5xl md:text-6xl text-center"
    >
      Nuestros Cursos
    </h2>
    <p class="max-w-2xl text-center text-accent/85">
      Potencia tus habilidades y aprende lo esencial del desarrollo web paso a
      paso.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-9 w-full max-w-6xl">
    <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold">Roadmap</h3>
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row gap-10">
      <div class="flex-1 flex-grow card min-h-[200px]">
        <ul class="timeline timeline-vertical">
          <li>
            <div class="timeline-start font-bold">Commit Master</div>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
              <CardIcon icon={Icons.GIT} />
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
            >
              9 de Septiembre
              <br />
              <p
                class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
              >
                Aprende a versionar y colaborar en proyectos de manera
                eficiente.
              </p>
            </div>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
          </li>

          <li>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
            <div class="timeline-start font-bold text-start">Dock It</div>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
              <CardIcon icon={Icons.DOCKER} />
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
            >
              11 de Septiembre
              <br />
              <p
                class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
              >
                Empaqueta y despliega aplicaciones en contenedores.
              </p>
            </div>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
          </li>

          <li>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
            <div class="timeline-start font-bold">Web Starter</div>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
              <StackIcon
                icons={[Icons.HTML, Icons.CSS, Icons.JAVASCRIPT]}
                size={40}
              />
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
            >
              Proximamente
              <br />
              <p
                class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
              >
                Construye sitios web interactivos desde cero.
              </p>
            </div>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
          </li>

          <li>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
            <div class="timeline-start font-bold">FigMagic</div>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
              <CardIcon icon={Icons.FIGMA} />
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
            >
              Proximamente
              <br />
              <p
                class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
              >
                Diseña interfaces y prototipos de forma rápida y profesional.
              </p>
            </div>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
          </li>

          <li>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-gradient-to-b from-info to-success" />
            <div class="timeline-start font-bold">Frontend Turbo</div>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
              <StackIcon icons={[Icons.ASTRO_WEB, Icons.TAILWIND]} size={40} />
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
            >
              Proximamente
              <br />
              <p
                class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
              >
                Crea sitios web modernos, rápidos y estilizados con Astro y
                Tailwind.
              </p>
            </div>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
          </li>

          <li>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
            <div class="timeline-start font-bold">Component Pro</div>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
              <StackIcon icons={[Icons.TYPESCRIPT, Icons.REACT]} size={40} />
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
            >
              Proximamente
              <br />
              <p
                class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
              >
                Desarrolla aplicaciones web robustas y tipadas con React y
                TypeScript.
              </p>
            </div>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
          </li>

          <li>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
            <div class="timeline-start font-bold">Backend Boost</div>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
              <CardIcon icon={Icons.NESTJS} />
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
            >
              Proximamente
              <br />
              <p
                class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
              >
                Construye APIs y backends escalables con NestJS.
              </p>
            </div>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
          </li>

          <li>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
            <div class="timeline-start font-bold">CodeVelocity</div>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
              <CardIcon icon={Icons.FAST_API} />
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
            >
              Proximamente
              <br />
              <p
                class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
              >
                Desarrolla APIs rápidas y modernas con Python y FastAPI.
              </p>
            </div>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
          </li>

          <li>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
            <div class="timeline-start font-bold">SupraFlow</div>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
              <CardIcon icon={Icons.SUPABASE} />
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
            >
              Proximamente
              <br />
              <p
                class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
              >
                Gestiona bases de datos y autenticación en la nube de forma
                sencilla.
              </p>
            </div>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-secondary" />
          </li>

          <li>
            <hr
              class="min-h-[20px] bg-gradient-to-b from-secondary to-primary"
            />
            <div class="timeline-start font-bold">DevUps</div>
            <div class="timeline-middle">
              <StackIcon
                icons={[
                  Icons.GITHUB_ACTIONS,
                  Icons.TERRAFORM,
                  Icons.KUBERNETES,
                ]}
                size={40}
              />
            </div>
            <div
              class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
            >
              Proximamente
              <br />
              <p
                class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
              >
                Automatiza, despliega y gestiona infraestructura en la nube
                profesionalmente.
              </p>
            </div>
            <hr class="min-h-[20px] bg-primary" />
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-0 md:flex-1 flex flex-col items-end gap-5 py-0 md:py-10">
        <p class="text-justify text-accent/90">
          Como grupo de estudio, hemos preparado un roadmap que te guiará en tu
          aprendizaje de desarrollo web. Si ya tienes conocimientos previos, no
          te preocupes: puedes unirte en la etapa que más te interese.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4">
          <div class="card text-neutral bg-info w-full shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title"><Iconify icon={Icons.BASIC} />Básico</h4>
              <p>
                Aprenderás los fundamentos de HTML, CSS y conceptos básicos de
                JavaScript. Esta etapa es ideal para quienes se inician en el
                desarrollo web.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card text-neutral bg-success w-full shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title">
                <Iconify icon={Icons.INTERMEDIATE} />Intermedio
              </h4>
              <p>
                Profundizarás en JavaScript, frameworks como React y buenas
                prácticas de desarrollo. Aquí aprenderás a crear aplicaciones
                más complejas y dinámicas.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="card text-neutral bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary w-full shadow-sm"
          >
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title">
                <Iconify icon={Icons.ADVANCED} />Avanzado
              </h4>
              <p>
                Te enfocarás en optimización, testing, arquitectura y despliegue
                de aplicaciones web. Esta etapa prepara para proyectos
                profesionales y trabajo en equipo.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
